20520_press_princelings|archive-date=2021-02-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>；并存在大量“[[裸官|裸官]]”，许多中央高层的子女或亲属移民海外或拥有外国[[永久居留證|绿卡]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=让“裸官”监管更加阳光|url=http://zqb.cyol.com/html/2012-02/21/nw.D110000zgqnb_20120221_1-03.htm|author=王亦君|date=2012-02-21|coauthors=董伟|work=《[[中国青年报|中国青年报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130123005729/http://zqb.cyol.com/html/2012-02/21/nw.D110000zgqnb_20120221_1-03.htm|archive-date=2013-01-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=知情者：官员移民美国无法融入当地社交圈|url=http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2014/0922/c1001-25708954.html|date=2014-09-22|work=[[人民网|人民网]]|publisher=《[[中国青年报|中国青年报]]》|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210801004951/http://politics.people.com.cn/n/2014/0922/c1001-25708954.html|archive-date=2021-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中国传密召高官子女回国恐再遭抵制|url=https://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20181005-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%8F%AC%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%9B%9E%E5%9B%BD%E6%81%90%E5%86%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6|author=小山|date=2018-10-05|work=[[法国国际广播电台|法国国际广播电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200223224906/http://www.rfi.fr/cn/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD/20181005-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BC%A0%E5%AF%86%E5%8F%AC%E9%AB%98%E5%AE%98%E5%AD%90%E5%A5%B3%E5%9B%9E%E5%9B%BD%E6%81%90%E5%86%8D%E9%81%AD%E6%8A%B5%E5%88%B6|archive-date=2020-02-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=中国部级以上官员儿孙辈大多有美国公民身份（图）|url=https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/fubai-02092011105333.html|date=2011-02-09|work=[[自由亚洲电台|自由亚洲电台]]|language=zh|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126115910/https://www.rfa.org/mandarin/yataibaodao/fubai-02092011105333.html|archive-date=2021-01-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

