://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/2184707/why-chinas-subsidised-state-owned-enterprises-anger-us-europe|author=Jane Cai|date=2019-02-21|work=《[[南华早报|南华早报]]》（South China Morning Post）|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210607210948/https://www.scmp.com/news/china/diplomacy/article/2184707/why-chinas-subsidised-state-owned-enterprises-anger-us-europe|archive-date=2021-06-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

